## Files Found
- `~/.pi/agent/extensions/orchestrator/delegate-tool.ts` — **main error swallowing site**
- `~/.pi/agent/extensions/orchestrator/subagent-runner.ts` — subagent execution + error surfacing
- `~/.pi/agent/extensions/orchestrator/debug.ts` — debug logger (itself swallows fs errors)
- `~/.pi/agent/extensions/orchestrator/activity-feed.ts` — `markFeedError()` error display
- `~/.pi/agent/extensions/orchestrator/plan-panel.ts` — `errorPlanStep()` error display
- `~/.pi/agent/extensions/orchestrator/index.ts` — entry point, no error handling
- `~/.pi/agent/extensions/scope-guard.ts` — scope enforcement, swallows parse errors

