- Trailing annotations: `- filesToModify: [] (read-only analysis)`
- Values are quoted: `- filesToModify: ["file.ts"]`

Fix the regex patterns for both filesToModify and filesToCreate:
```typescript
const modifyMatch = section.match(/-?\s*\*{0,2}filesToModify\*{0,2}:\s*\[([^\]]*)\]/);
const createMatch = section.match(/-?\s*\*{0,2}filesToCreate\*{0,2}:\s*\[([^\]]*)\]/);
